// 文章卡片组件（占位示例）
---
<div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-4 shadow-md flex flex-col gap-2 transition-colors duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
  <div class="font-semibold text-lg text-text-primary">[文章标题]</div>
  <div class="text-text-secondary text-xs">2025-05-20</div>
  <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm line-clamp-2">这里是文章摘要或内容预览。你可以在这里展示文章简介、标签等。</div>
  <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2 text-text-secondary text-xs">
    <span class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200">👍 20</span>
    <span class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200">💬 5</span>
    <span class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200">🔗 阅读</span>
  </div>
</div>
